Name: Clear Sky
Desc: The stars will not know the answer to the future, but they can tell you that tomorrow will be a great day.

Name: Emergency Training
Desc: Alien planets also have training fields. It is no surprise that you can find one.

Name: Arctic Tears
Desc: One will suffer the same pain from extreme cold and heat.

Name: Magnetic Blast
Desc: Tick, tock. Time flows with life.

Name: Gingerbread King Parfait
Desc: The adorable king blesses all its people equally.

Name: Only One
Desc: Yes, there is only one. Going from zero to one can be considered a great breakthrough even on a cosmic scale.

Name: Two More!
Desc: "I can't let this opportunity slip away... Wait, my space ship!"

Name: Blessing From the Best Warrior
Desc: "The greatest strength is right in your heart."
